<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>2455</hymn_number>
<author>ạ̉mạny smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<title>jwʿny lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- jwʿny lyk wạsẖbʿny byk .. ạsẖbʿny rby bfyḍ gẖnạk
 flạ ạ̉ḥtạj fy ạ̉y ḍyq .. (ạ̉n ạ̉bḥtẖ ʿn swạk)2
 2- ạmlạ ʿyny bjmạl yswʿ .. wạgẖsl kẖyạly bjrwḥ yswʿ
 flạ ạ̉ḥtạj fy ạ̉y jwʿ .. (ạ̉n ạ̉sẖbʿ mn swạk)2
 3- ạmsḥ dmwʿy ạ̹brỷ jrwḥy .. ạ̹nt sẖfạỷy ʿzạʾ rwḥy
 nsẖyd qlby htạf ʿmry .. (ạ̹lhy lys swạk)2</lyrics>
</song>